file.name: minimal.yaml
file.content:
# Minimum valid openapi 3 spec

openapi: 3.0.0

info:
  title: Minimum API Test
  version: 1.0.0

paths:
  /endpoint-1:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK

components:
  headers:
    content-type:
      schema:
        type: string
        example: application/json
  securitySchemes:
    BearerJWT:
      description: |
        Bearer token JWT
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: "eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJhdXRoSW........."
